      "id": "PopularPost261128",
      "post_content": "5 cost? I wish this guy was JUST. ONE. LESS. :P  \n  \nI like him a lot, but I'm not going to build mono-red dragons when I could build Scion Rainbow Dragons or Kaalia Dragons Angels Demons. So for my real dragons decks I'd wish he could be played a little faster :/  \n  \nI think I'd rather play Dragonspeaker Shaman, because I'm not sure yet how much percent of my deck I'm going to let be Red. If it turns out very Red, Zirilan is probably better, but there is a legitimate issue of color density because of the other cards I want to play.  \n  \nObviously, if colors are not something you see being an issue because you aren't interested in doing anything except straightforward Dragons Are Awesome, then go ahead and autoinclude him. ",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost261128\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">5 cost? I wish this guy was JUST. ONE. LESS. :P<br/><br/>I like him a lot, but I'm not going to build mono-red dragons when I could build Scion Rainbow Dragons or Kaalia Dragons Angels Demons. So for my real dragons decks I'd wish he could be played a little faster :/<br/><br/>I think I'd rather play Dragonspeaker Shaman, because I'm not sure yet how much percent of my deck I'm going to let be Red. If it turns out very Red, Zirilan is probably better, but there is a legitimate issue of color density because of the other cards I want to play.<br/><br/>Obviously, if colors are not something you see being an issue because you aren't interested in doing anything except straightforward Dragons Are Awesome, then go ahead and autoinclude him. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '261128'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (8/5/2012 2:21:05 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"star