      "id": "PopularPost334020",
      "post_content": "[Hellkite Tyrant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hellkite Tyrant): steal one player's artifacts  \n[Furnace Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Furnace Dragon): exile all player's artifacts  \n[Utvara Hellkite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Utvara Hellkite): leaves one or more friends behind  \n[Malfegor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Malfegor): discard your hand and kill lots of creatures  \n[Thunder Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thunder Dragon): 3 damage to all ground-pounders  \n**[Worldgorger Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worldgorger Dragon): only costs 9 mana to run this with [Jokulhaups](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jokulhaups).**  \n  \nTry [Erratic Portal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Erratic Portal) to save your dragons.",
      "posted_by": "kiseki",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost334020\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hellkite Tyrant\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hellkite Tyrant\">Hellkite Tyrant</a>: steal one player's artifacts<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Furnace Dragon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Furnace Dragon\">Furnace Dragon</a>: exile all player's artifacts<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Utvara Hellkite\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Utvara Hellkite\">Utvara Hellkite</a>: leaves one or more friends behind<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Malfegor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Malfegor\">Malfegor</a>: discard your hand and kill lots of creatures<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thunder Dragon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thunder Dragon\">Thunder Dragon</a>: 3 damage to all ground-pounders<br/><b><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Worldgorger Dragon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worldgorger Dragon\">Worldgorger Dragon</a>: only costs 9 mana to run this with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jokulhaups\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jokulhaups\">Jokulhaups</a>.</b><br/><br/>Try <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Erratic Portal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Erratic Portal\">Erratic Portal</a> to save your dragons.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '334020'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Re